ies\nstill contribute significantly to the current uncertainty in $\\tau$, but all\nvalues are consistent with the range of $\\tau$ = 0.07 +/- 0.02.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 4 Jan 2018 02:25:55 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 10 Jan 2018 21:14:46 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Tue, 8 Jan 2019 18:17:44 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-01-09"}
