isson equation with a time step much larger than the particle\ncollision time. Highly non-equilibrium and rarefied plasma flows, such as\nelectron flows driven by electromagnetic field, can be simulated easily.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 4 Jan 2018 12:50:40 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 16 Jan 2018 07:41:41 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-10-18"}
